Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.84,0:00:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为集齐了5位部员 请批准歌牌部开始正式活动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.70,0:00:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.34,0:00:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.39,0:00:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.58,0:00:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是部长必须改成绫濑同学以外的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.70,0:00:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顾问暂时由我来担任
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.31,0:00:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 解散
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.65,0:00:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我就不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.26,0:00:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 也许是明智的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.78,0:00:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 部长怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真岛就好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.21,0:00:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸 我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.59,0:00:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.26,0:00:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.95,0:00:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话千早…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.95,0:00:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那我来担任队长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.72,0:00:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.39,0:02:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部费三千日圆？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.17,0:02:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买了歌牌之后就一点不剩了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.73,0:02:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起练习方法 我们怎么进行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.40,0:02:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先我和真岛交换著做绫濑的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.59,0:02:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空閒的那个就教小奏和桌子君怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.22,0:02:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫勉 肉包君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.08,0:02:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}<桌子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.81,0:02:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}肉包>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.82,0:02:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为千早已经是A级了 \N就和其他两人实行不同的训练方式
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.46,0:02:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 A级有那么厉害吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初从E级开始 在大会中优胜之后升级
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.20,0:02:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺带一说 我和西田是B级
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.47,0:03:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然根据所属的歌牌会会有所不同
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.40,0:03:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要升A级一般必须在大会中优胜或者获得2次准优胜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.81,0:03:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸？是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.23,0:03:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！今天要和小奏和桌子君对战咯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.16,0:03:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要跟驹野和大江同学比赛吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.58,0:03:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说些什么呀 就算和A级的你进行比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.74,0:03:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也根本成不了初心者的练习
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我要这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们2个也不会觉得有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我还是要这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.63,0:03:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.47,0:03:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为部长和队长哪个更厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.85,0:03:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸？到底是谁呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.49,0:03:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\be3\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(750,80)\frz270\fn@方正大标宋_GBK\fad(300,600)}第九首
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.49,0:03:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\be3\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(650,240)\fn@方正准圆_GBK\frz270\fad(300,600)}欲掩不从心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.76,0:03:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}いまをはるべと　さくやこのはな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.76,0:03:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今兮春满地 花开香芬芳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.93,0:03:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}いまをはるべと　さくやこのはな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.93,0:03:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今兮春满地 花开香芬芳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.32,0:03:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}おとにきく
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.32,0:03:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高师海浪美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}ゆふされば
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暮色门前降
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.37,0:04:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 毫不留情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}あしのまろやに あきかぜぞふく
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摇摇鸣稻叶 芦舍临秋风
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.80,0:04:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}さびしさに
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.80,0:04:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂寞门前立
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早 果然还是不行 实力差太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.19,0:04:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小奏 我第一次玩歌牌的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.26,0:04:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手也是一个超级厉害的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他放水的话我就不会变得那么喜欢歌牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.19,0:04:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也不会放水 以全力来进行比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.93,0:04:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望大家变得更强
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.87,0:05:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在暑假以我们五人打入团体赛的全国大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近江神宫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么是近江神宫？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定日本高中生歌牌第一的比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年的4月 在滋贺县的近江神宫裡举行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.86,0:05:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也被称作歌牌的甲子园
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是在东京预赛裡取得优胜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.41,0:05:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后就是全国大赛了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优胜 全国大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.38,0:05:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 会有多少学校来参加东京预赛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.36,0:05:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为东京是激战区啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.39,0:05:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不可能的 进全国大赛什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们才刚刚起步
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.80,0:05:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的 我每天都会全力的做桌子君和小奏的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.40,0:05:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们可要做好觉悟哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.70,0:06:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 千早
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸 你指的什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是做驹野和大江同学的对手的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.00,0:06:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己就不能练习了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.99,0:06:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事的话没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.52,0:06:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么没问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是以个人战优胜为目标吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.22,0:06:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社团你就别管了 去白波会练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.43,0:06:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和西田会做他们两人的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.18,0:06:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.69,0:06:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们和新三个人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.17,0:06:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次参加比赛的事情还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.59,0:06:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像那个时候一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想跟大家组成团队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.57,0:06:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.27,0:06:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是定位置
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.20,0:06:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定位置？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:07:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 就是事先决定好的自阵的配置
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.91,0:07:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次比赛的时候 我们不可能将牌的位置百分百的记下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经大致决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.83,0:07:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将喜欢的牌重点摆在右下段
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.55,0:07:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.71,0:07:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像大江同学那样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将「はるす」和「はるの」摆在一起的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然自己很容易抢到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是对手也是很容易抢到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.24,0:07:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.30,0:07:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是说这么做不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.89,0:07:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你的直觉比对方要好的话是可以抢到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.37,0:07:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何才能让自己容易的抢到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.54,0:07:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何才能使对方很难抢到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.61,0:07:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练习上几百次后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.41,0:07:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将只属于自己的配置用身体牢牢的记住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.25,0:07:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先最重要的是经验
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来比赛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.11,0:07:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是左撇子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.57,0:07:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以可以把自己喜欢的牌放在左边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.79,0:07:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么简单可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大山牌当中有理论吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.94,0:07:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有16张之多的「あ」的牌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.04,0:07:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也请教教我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:07:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加天衣无缝的配置
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.06,0:08:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想输给后面进来的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.68,0:08:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}なほあまりある むかしなりけり
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.68,0:08:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繁华思旧岁 切切断人肠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.65,0:08:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}はなさそふ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.65,0:08:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满院非白雪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.03,0:08:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}しらつゆに
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.03,0:08:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清秋原野上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.95,0:08:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}いにしへの
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.95,0:08:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古都奈良城
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.57,0:08:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}わがいほは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.57,0:08:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我住皇都外
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}みよしのの やまのあきかぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故国秋风起 萧萧吉野山
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 空牌 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不用道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.47,0:08:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失败也是一种经验啊经验
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}おほえやま
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山长平野阔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.20,0:08:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.11,0:08:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抢…抢到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.87,0:08:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次抢到的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.27,0:08:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 小奏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.30,0:08:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.60,0:08:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.45,0:08:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下过决心 今天一定要抢到这张牌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.67,0:09:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 好厉害啊 哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.59,0:09:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新 我终于也有同伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.51,0:09:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.29,0:09:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新给我的东西在渐渐扩散哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.47,0:09:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离校时间早就过了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.86,0:09:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点给我回家去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.30,0:09:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 练习时间根本不够
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.31,0:09:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上完课之后只能比赛2场左右
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说根本就不够
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更重要的是没法锻炼耐力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.06,0:09:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到参加比赛的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.01,0:09:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天要比赛4场以上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.83,0:09:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 在白波会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天的时候 会在河口湖举行2晚左右的合宿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.87,0:09:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来那个是为了锻炼耐力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.76,0:09:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.21,0:09:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好啊 合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.45,0:09:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也来办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.71,0:09:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下週的週六週日因为是创校纪念 所以连休哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.34,0:09:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:09:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在哪裡办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.13,0:10:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又能留宿又能练习歌牌的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离比赛还有三週
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考虑到寻找场地浪费的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.85,0:10:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不如练习一场比赛比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.91,0:10:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把午休和放学时间有效的利用起来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多少也会起点作用的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 附近能够让大家都留宿的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.79,0:10:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那么简单能找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.21,0:10:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太幸运了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.39,0:10:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一的父母去神户参加婚礼去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创校纪念日和星期日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以一整天玩歌牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以使用和室 棉被也够你们几个人盖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.48,0:10:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过真的连千早也要留下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.57,0:10:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是队长嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.45,0:10:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.74,0:10:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.02,0:10:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大家来之前 让我参观一下太一的房间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.74,0:10:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前我们不是经常一起玩电玩的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.38,0:11:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你家裡人不是又给你买了大电视吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.96,0:11:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看 让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.96,0:11:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人的房间不是随便能进的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.28,0:11:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不会让你进去的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真岛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.25,0:11:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出生以来第一次感受到贫富差距…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个 那样东西买来了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.70,0:11:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过合宿感觉让人心跳不已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭怎么办呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.99,0:11:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有试胆会吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.34,0:11:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个不错耶 附近会有墓地吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.51,0:12:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些全部都是真岛的?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.60,0:12:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英语准1级 小提琴 骑马 滑雪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.07,0:12:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.44,0:12:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 因为父母喜欢让我学这学那…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.67,0:12:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 千早那傢伙竟然把这种多馀的东西给人看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.26,0:12:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 这位是真岛的妈妈?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美丽的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.92,0:12:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是我不擅长应付她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.41,0:12:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.55,0:12:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么没赢得第一的话就会被她骂的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.08,0:12:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我称呼她压力夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.75,0:12:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不是来练习的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.37,0:12:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么现在我宣佈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.17,0:12:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞泽高中歌牌部第一回合宿的目标是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在今天和明天这两天内比15场比赛!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.18,0:12:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.19,0:12:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对战表我都做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:12:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千 千早 这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.58,0:13:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么都是我和桌子君在比啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.48,0:13:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 现在最重要的是实战
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一场比赛都要集中精神去比哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小奏 你的手挥得太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.59,0:13:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才教你的姿势 没有做到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桌子君 那裡要用按的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.20,0:13:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神再集中一点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.95,0:13:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你们能变强
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.97,0:13:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想让你们赢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.48,0:13:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想让你们赢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.13,0:13:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就只有好好练习了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看 接著是桌子君对肉包君 小奏对…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.02,0:13:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.96,0:13:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.66,0:13:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天先到这裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊 才比了五场比赛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.34,0:13:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}ながらへば またこのごろや しのばれむ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.34,0:13:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若得人长在 今朝亦留痕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.97,0:14:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}うしとみしよぞ いまはこひしき
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.97,0:14:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往事虽悲苦 件件可追寻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.72,0:14:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果人能一直长存的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受到痛苦的现在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会成为令人怀念的追忆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.26,0:14:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们两人已经到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.30,0:14:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是到了比赛的时候 就会有许多难受的情况啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.23,0:14:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以必须继续练习才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.59,0:14:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.05,0:14:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想累垮拼命努力的人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之今天先到此为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.40,0:14:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.23,0:14:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸亏真岛是部长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个还不吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.59,0:14:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有食慾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.67,0:14:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.71,0:14:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不吃的话就坚持不下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桌子君 努力吃去下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.47,0:15:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天也需要练习的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.91,0:15:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桌子君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小奏 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.62,0:15:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.69,0:15:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了 快躲起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.84,0:15:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀太一 你朋友来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天不是在那边过夜吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.86,0:15:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪梨香突然说想要回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.06,0:15:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}USJ：Universal Studios Japan的缩写 \N是位于大坂市的好莱坞电影主题公园 2001年开设
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.06,0:15:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不去USJ 就没有任何意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.69,0:15:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}梨香真是任性
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真危险啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绕到玄关拿回鞋子 然后到我家去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.50,0:15:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压力夫人是不可能答应让女孩子留下来过夜的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小奏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.79,0:16:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想累垮拼命努力的人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.06,0:16:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说我经常被人说…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.67,0:16:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「千早眼中只有花牌」什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.51,0:16:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真没用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.36,0:16:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没用…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.07,0:16:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.30,0:16:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧 千早
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.59,0:16:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等一下 小奏?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.73,0:16:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 小奏?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.05,0:16:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三更半夜 要去哪裡啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.05,0:16:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 我说小奏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.55,0:17:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 要跑到哪裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.68,0:17:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂～　千早 这裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.39,0:17:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一? 大家也在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.10,0:17:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉在这种时候叫你过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我们今晚无论如何也有话想跟队长说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.30,0:17:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.26,0:17:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我先说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.54,0:17:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.07,0:17:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.33,0:17:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 完全没有看到周围
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.99,0:17:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得大家都在努力了 我还勉强大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.50,0:17:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.56,0:17:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关係啦 绫濑这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.56,0:17:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.21,0:17:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强硬是绫濑的性格 有一个这样的人在也挺不错的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.31,0:17:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉包君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:17:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:18:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为有对歌牌专心一志的千早在…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.54,0:18:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家才会想要努力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.47,0:18:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小奏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还有很多不懂的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.20,0:18:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我好像也会喜欢上歌牌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.51,0:18:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桌子君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.21,0:18:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.22,0:18:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 快点吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在真岛妈妈洗完澡之前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.77,0:18:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 忘了拿刀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.93,0:18:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这是调羹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.39,0:18:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 就这么吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.46,0:18:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样 太没礼貌了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.27,0:18:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 千早巧克力块
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.76,0:18:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点吃快点吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.83,0:18:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.69,0:18:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这黄色的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.12,0:18:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的份
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.57,0:18:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早也快点来吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.78,0:19:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.49,0:19:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你笑了 歌牌才会有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.20,0:19:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的哦 队长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢蛋糕的皮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.67,0:19:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能把一圈都吃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.48,0:19:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.40,0:19:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.77,0:19:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是千早的生日 当然可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.91,0:19:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.46,0:19:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.33,0:19:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过真岛的妈妈还真是有点可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.58,0:19:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁去给浴室上个锁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.76,0:19:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.98,0:19:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.92,0:19:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.31,0:19:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陌生地址
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.63,0:20:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.26,0:20:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把最后一口蛋糕皮给你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.99,0:20:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人 才不给你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.56,0:20:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过真岛的妈妈真的很可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.89,0:20:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 流星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.24,0:20:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.79,0:20:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是第一次看见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.34,0:21:00.34,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn方正准圆_GBK}{\fs26}{\1a&H6E&\1c&H704338&}{\be1}{\frz7}{\pos(300,280)\fad(200,600)\bord0}太一 之前抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.34,0:21:00.34,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn方正准圆_GBK}{\fs26}{\1a&H6E&\1c&H704338&}{\be1}{\frz7}{\pos(320,310)\bord0\fad(200,600)}替我向千早说声生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.74,0:20:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,16岁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.15,0:21:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是我过的最好的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.37,0:21:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 又有了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.51,0:21:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.55,0:21:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡 在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.49,0:21:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.85,0:21:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.16,0:01:11.44,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}帰り道は过ぎていく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:14.82,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}少し风が吹いている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.92,0:01:19.99,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}たわいない会话妙に楽しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.41,0:01:24.87,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}今でも変わらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.05,0:01:28.61,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}僕ら待ち合わせたあの场所
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.83,0:01:33.98,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}君はまだ覚えてるのかな?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.10,0:01:41.82,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}今はちはやふる想い胸に抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.94,0:01:47.16,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}目指した先に何があるんだ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.26,0:01:52.94,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}今なら掴めそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.02,0:01:55.82,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}手を伸ばしてみる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.94,0:02:02.35,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}梦の途中きっといつかまた会えるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.16,0:01:11.44,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}慢步走过回家的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:14.82,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}微风轻轻吹拂著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.92,0:01:19.99,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}閒话家常也异常有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.41,0:01:24.87,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}至今依旧一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.05,0:01:28.61,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}我们常常相约等候的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.83,0:01:33.98,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}你可否仍然记得呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.10,0:01:41.82,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}现在我心怀强烈的嚮往
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.94,0:01:47.16,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}有什么在目标之处
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.26,0:01:52.94,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}现在的话似乎能抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.02,0:01:55.82,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}试著伸出双手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.94,0:02:02.35,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}在梦想的路上终有一天会再度重逢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:29.61,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}そしていま ふたりは
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.75,0:21:34.52,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}远すぎる世界见つめて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.71,0:21:40.07,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}そしていま ほら 响くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:47.35,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}君が教えてくれた歌 この空で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.51,0:21:52.48,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}そしていま わたしは
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.62,0:21:57.48,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}君に続く空见上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.64,0:22:02.90,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}そしていま まだ歌うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.04,0:22:07.65,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}どこにいたって届くはずだって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.84,0:22:12.83,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}そしていま ふたりは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.97,0:22:17.88,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}辉く明日を见つめて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.03,0:22:23.36,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}そしていま ほら 响くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.54,0:22:31.77,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}君が教えてくれた歌 この空に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:29.61,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}于是此刻你我两人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.75,0:21:34.52,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}凝望著遥不可及的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.71,0:21:40.07,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}于是此刻 你听 歌声响彻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:47.35,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}你曾经教会我唱的歌谣  迴响在这片天空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.51,0:21:52.48,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}于是此刻 我举头仰望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.62,0:21:57.48,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}延伸到你身旁的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.64,0:22:02.90,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}于是此刻 依然歌唱著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.04,0:22:07.65,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}无论身处何方也应该传递得到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.84,0:22:12.83,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}于是此刻你我两人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.97,0:22:17.88,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}凝望著光辉闪烁的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.03,0:22:23.36,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}于是此刻 你听 歌声响彻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.54,0:22:31.77,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}你曾经教会我唱的歌谣 迴响于这片天空
